        "titolo_orig": "Enough gerrymandering — the people must take back power from two-party rule",
        "testo_it": "Gerrymandering: Corte Suprema USA permette mappa elettorale pro-Democrat in California.",
        "priorita": "Media",
        "id_gruppo": 22,
        "link": "https://thehill.com/opinion/judiciary/5769192-supreme-court-gerrymandering-decision/",
        "orario": "13:30",
        "timestamp": 1772800200,
        "contenuto_esteso": "The Supreme Court’s recent decision allowing California to proceed with a politically gerrymandered map favoring Democrats may be, as the headlines proclaimed, a victory for Democrats, just as the Texas map gerrymandered in favor of Republicans was considered a victory for Republicans. Taken together, however, they undermine the foundations of American republican democracy."
